description:
In the final issue of TMNT Classics Digest the Foot Clan is at war with itself! On one side it's Shredder, Rocksteady and Bebop, while on the other side it's Krang and his new allies Slash and Bellybomb, and the TMNT are caught in the middle! 
 
Featuring guest appearances by: 
Shredder, Bebop, Rocksteady, Krang, Foot Soldier, Slash, Bellybomb, April O'Neil and Master Splinter
name: TMNTA 23-25
